Description: use export-safe ACPI handle traversal on modern kernels
 Replace direct struct acpi_device child traversal and GPL-only helper calls with
 acpi_walk_namespace() handle traversal when acpi_device internals are absent.
Origin: backport, NVIDIA ACPI handle-based compatibility adapted to 367.134
Forwarded: not-needed
Last-Update: 2026-07-20

